    "A summary of this study is presented in Table 4.",
    "The system combined the attention mechanism with the knowledge tracing model and used both student exercise features and behavioral features.",
    "In addition, the feature representation was automatically captured using ML approaches.",
    "The exercise and behavioral features of the students were handled using the PCA approach.",
    "Next, student performance was predicted using a fusion attention technique based on RNN architecture (LSTM)."
